headline: Coinbase, Robinhood Stocks Fall. Why It’s a Volatile Day for Crypto Shares.
summary: Coinbase Global Robinhood Markets  and other crypto-related stocks slipped early Tuesday as Bitcoin’s blistering rally appeared to take a pause.  Stocks exposed to cryptos had a volatile start to premarket trading.  Exchange  Coinbase  trading platform  Robinhood  Markets, and Bitcoin-buyer  MicroStrategy  were all up more than 5% initially.
